itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson, Jarred Taylor, and Dan Hollaway welcome back Milo Yiannopoulos live from a Holiday Inn in Newark, NJ as Milo agrees to help JT take on a male partner in 2020, what it's like as a white guy having an all black Christmas at your house, why the holidays are "bulking season", and Milo gives himself Drinkin' Bro of the week. Hilarious episode.
